## Shared Components Architecture

### Sidebar Component

```mermaid
graph LR
    subgraph PortalSidebar
        THEME[Portal Config<br/>Color, Icon, Label]
        USER[User Info<br/>Name, Role, Avatar]
        MENU[Navigation Menu<br/>Role-based items]
        AI[AI Assistant<br/>Floating bubble]
        FOOTER[Footer<br/>Logout, Settings]
    end

    THEME --> MENU
    USER --> FOOTER
```

**Portal Config (`src/config/portal-config.ts`):**
```typescript
export const portalConfig = {
  student: {
    name: "Student Portal",
    color: "rgb(249 115 22)",
    icon: "GraduationCap",
    gradient: "from-orange-500 to-red-500"
  },
  teacher: {
    name: "Teacher Portal",
    color: "rgb(59 130 246)",
    icon: "ChalkboardTeacher",
    gradient: "from-blue-500 to-indigo-500"
  },
  // ... etc
}
```

### AI Assistant Component

```mermaid
graph LR
    subgraph UnifiedAIAssistant
        ROLE[User Role Detection]
        PROMPT[Role-Specific Prompt]
        MODEL[AI Model]
        UI[Themed Chat UI]
    end

    ROLE --> PROMPT
    PROMPT --> MODEL
    MODEL --> UI
```

**Role-Specific AI:**
| Role | AI Name | Theme | Specialization |
|------|---------|-------|----------------|
| Student | Career Coach | Orange | Career guidance, study tips |
| Teacher | Teacher Assistant | Blue | Lesson planning, assessments |
| Parent | Parent Guide | Gray | Child development, fees |
| Counselor | Wellness Guide | Purple | Mental health, interventions |
| School Admin | Admin Helper | Violet | School management |
| Platform Admin | System Assistant | Pink | Platform oversight |
| Ministry | Policy Advisor | Indigo | Education policy |

