## Layout Hierarchy

```
src/app/
├── layout.tsx                    # Root layout (ToastProvider, theme)
├── [portal]/
│   └── layout.tsx                # Dynamic portal layout (7 portals)
├── admin/
│   └── layout.tsx                # Admin-specific layout
├── parent/
│   └── layout.tsx                # Parent-specific layout
├── student/                      # Uses [portal] layout
│   ├── dashboard/page.tsx
│   ├── classes/page.tsx
│   └── ...
├── teacher/                      # Uses [portal] layout
├── counselor/                    # Uses [portal] layout
├── school-admin/                 # Uses [portal] layout
├── ministry/                     # Uses [portal] layout
└── setup/
    └── unified/page.tsx          # Unified setup wizard
```

