## Responsive Design Strategy

### Desktop (> 1024px)
- Full sidebar navigation
- Horizontal header
- Multi-column layouts
- Hover interactions

### Tablet (768px - 1024px)
- Collapsible sidebar
- Optimized tables
- Touch-friendly controls

### Mobile (< 768px)
- Bottom navigation bar
- Full-screen modals
- Swipe gestures
- Single column layouts
